metadata.title: totes Girls Boys Kids Cozy Warm Soft Toddler Child Slipper Sock with Non-Slip Grips and Fun Cute Dino/Unicorn design, 2 Pack

SOFT AND COZY: Keep your kids toes and feet warm while they play! These lightweight and super comfortable cotton blend socks will keep your kids warm while they run and have fun around the house
NON SLIP SOCK: Slip resistant anti skid silicone dot tread helps manage slips and falls so playtime never has to end
MOISTURE WICKING: Made of high quality cotton and nylon for flexibility, these socks wick away moisture keeping little feet dry during a dayâ€™s activities
AT HOME LEARNING FOOTWEAR: Perfect socks for at home learning, if your little ones are at home in zoom classes, help keep their feet nice and warm while they learn
description: Double the fun with this incredibly adorable, 2-pack of animal themed slipper socks! Grippy bottom tread helps manage slips and falls to protect kids as they play around the house. While the lightweight and super comfortable fabric will keep your kids warm as they play and have fun. When the little ones are finally tuckered out, simply toss the socks in the washing machine and they're ready for another adventured filled day. Perfect gift for your child, these will be the socks your kids will want to wear every day!
